OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FThe former chief executive of the
OL,7,Fhospital trust where baby killer Lucy
OL,8,FLetby worked has been awarded #1.4
OL,9,Fmillion in damages after winning a
OL,10,Flandmark employment tribunal for
OL,11,Funfair dismissal.
OL,13,FDr Susan Gilby was promoted to the top
OL,14,Fpost at the Countess of Chester NHS
OL,15,FTrust just weeks after Letby was
OL,16,Farrested in 2018.
