OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FBut the tribunal heard that after
OL,7,Flodging a formal whistleblowing
OL,8,Fcomplaint against the trust's chairman
OL,9,Fin 2022, she was the victim of
OL,10,F'appalling treatment' that led to her
OL,11,Funfair dismissal.
OL,13,FDr Gilby had accused chairman Ian
OL,14,FHaythornthwaite of bullying and
OL,15,Fharassment.
OL,17,FThe payout is one of the largest
OL,18,Fpayments the NHS has ever made to an
OL,19,Fex-NHS employee.
