OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FIn a cover-up attempt to silence her,
OL,7,Fthe tribunal heard how the Countess of
OL,8,FChester management had set up
OL,9,Fsomething they dubbed 'Project
OL,10,FCountess', where they reportedly
OL,11,Fpurged "hundreds of messages and
OL,12,Fdocuments" in an alleged bid to evade
OL,13,Faccountability.
OL,15,FDr Gilby lodged her formal whistle-
OL,16,Fblowing complaint in July 2022 against
OL,17,Fthe chairman, voicing her concerns
OL,18,Fabout his conduct to both the NHS
OL,19,Ftrust and NHS England.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
