OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FIn response to her allegations, Dr
OL,7,FGilby stated the trust offered her a
OL,8,Fsecondment to a high-level advisory
OL,9,Fposition within NHS England on the
OL,10,Fprovision that she withdraw her
OL,11,Faccusations. Subsequently, NHS England
OL,12,Fapproached her regarding a role.
OL,14,FDr Gilby, however, in November,
OL,15,Fdeclined to retract her claims, and
OL,16,Fwas suspended by the trust on 2
OL,17,FDecember.
OL,19,FFollowing this, on 5 December, she
OL,20,Fnotified the trust of her decision to
OL,21,Fresign after a six-month notice period.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
