OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FSpeaking about her treatment by the
OL,7,FCountess of Chester NHS Trust and the
OL,8,Foutcome of her Employment Tribunal, Dr
OL,9,FSusan Gilby said: "I am deeply
OL,10,Fsaddened that having raised a
OL,11,Fprotected disclosure in good faith, I
OL,12,Fwas treated in such an appalling
OL,13,Fmanner that I had no choice other than
OL,14,Fto seek justice through the Employment
OL,15,FTribunal.
OL,17,F"I am yet to receive any meaningful
OL,18,Fapology from the Trust for the harm
OL,19,Fcaused to me or for the needless
OL,20,Fending of my career.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
