OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,F"I am extremely grateful to the BMA
OL,7,Ffor their support. They enabled me to
OL,8,Fpursue justice in the face of an
OL,9,Forganisation prepared to spend
OL,10,Fextraordinary sums to silence me. I am
OL,11,Falso indebted to my legal team led by
OL,12,FIan Radford and Oliver Segal KC.
OL,14,F"What is clear is that the BMA are not
OL,15,Fjust there to help doctors with pay or
OL,16,Fterms and conditions, they are there
OL,17,Fto support doctors and protect us
OL,18,Fthrough the most difficult and
OL,19,Fchallenging circumstances ` other
OL,20,Fdoctors should feel encouraged by this.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
