OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,F"The Trust has failed to condemn
OL,7,Funequivocally, the actions of Ian
OL,8,FHaythornthwaite and the members of the
OL,9,Fboard who colluded with him in these
OL,10,Fmatters. I did everything I could to
OL,11,Finform senior leaders in the NHS all
OL,12,Fthe way to the top, of the reality of
OL,13,Fthe situation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
