OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,F"They choose to do nothing. These
OL,7,Funacceptable behaviours, along with
OL,8,Ftheir conduct of the case, has damaged
OL,9,Fnot only me but also the taxpayer who
OL,10,Fhas every right to expect custodians
OL,11,Fof the public purse to act in their
OL,12,Fbest interests and not in the pursuit
OL,13,Fof cheque book litigation.
OL,15,F"The settlement sum compensates me for
OL,16,Flost salary and pension as well as
OL,17,Fincluding a sum for personal injury.
OL,18,FHowever, no amount of money can
OL,19,Fcompensate me for the devastation of
OL,20,Flosing my career in this appalling
OL,21,Fmanner."
OL,26,@wD@AOU
