OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,FHer case was supported by the British
OL,7,FMedical Association (BMA), who
OL,8,Fdescribed this as a landmark case.
OL,10,FThe BMA also warned of the need to
OL,11,Fchange the 'shameful treatment' of
OL,12,Fwhistleblowers in the NHS , and called
OL,13,Ffor a transformation of the 'corrosive
OL,14,FNHS culture' that is more concerned
OL,15,Fwith reputation rather than patient
OL,16,Fsafety.
