OL,6,FBMA Council chair Dr Tom Dolphin said
OL,7,F"While this award is significant and a
OL,8,Ftestament to the determination and
OL,9,Fbravery of Dr Susan Gilby, it comes at
OL,10,Fthe end of an arduous and distressing
OL,11,Fjourney for a doctor who was unfairly
OL,12,Fpenalised for refusing to stay quiet
OL,13,Fabout the failings she saw.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
