OL,3,CLandmark case sees ex CEO of Letby
OL,4,Ctrust awarded massive payout
OL,6,F"The BMA has supported Dr Gilby
OL,7,Fthroughout her case to bring the
OL,8,Fappalling behaviour of those
OL,9,Fresponsible for her treatment at the
OL,10,FCountess of Chester - this should
OL,11,Fserve as a warning to others that the
OL,12,Fshameful treatment of whistleblowers
OL,13,Fcan lead to consequences in the law
OL,14,Fcourts.
OL,16,F"It is disappointing that despite the
OL,17,Ffinancial award, the trust is refusing
OL,18,Fto issue an apology for its damaging
OL,19,Fconduct.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
