OL,6,F"The horrific scale of this cover-up
OL,7,Fshows the length that some trusts are
OL,8,Fwilling to go to in an attempt to
OL,9,Fsilence doctors and the very real
OL,10,Fthreat that unfortunately remains for
OL,11,Fmany working in the NHS who want to
OL,12,Fraise concerns about patient safety."
OL,14,FThe Countess of Chester NHS Trust has
OL,15,Fbeen contacted for comment.
